module_connect_description: Power up and plug in the required module(s) via the OT-2 USB Ports. Place the modules as shown in the deck map.
module_connect_duplicate_description: Plug the modules in to the USB ports as listed in the Placement and Calibration Panel. Check out our help docs for more information on using modules of the same type.
module_connect_instruction: Plug the modules in to the USB ports as listed below, from left to right.
module_connect_missing_tooltip: Connect module(s) to proceed to labware calibration
modules_update_software_tooltip: Update robot software to see USB port information
